YOU HAVE TO CONTINUE
INTO COLLEGE,

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:31.000
WHICH IS GOOD, FOR SOME SENSE,

00:15:31.000 --> 00:15:33.000
BUT THEY'RE ALSO
CLOSING DOORS FOR US,

00:15:33.000 --> 00:15:35.000
BECAUSE WHEN WE GO
TO THE UNIVERSITY,

00:15:35.000 --> 00:15:37.000
THEY'RE ALSO TELLING US,
NOW YOU GOTTA PAY MORE MONEY

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:40.000
FOR THE SAME EDUCATION
THAT OTHER IMMIGRANTS HAD.

