BUT IT'S CERTAINLY TRUE
THAT FROM WHAT I'VE SEEN,

00:15:50.000 --> 00:15:52.000
FIREMEN AND POLICEMEN ARE USING

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:55.000
PRETTY SOPHISTICATED MACHINERY
THESE DAYS.

00:15:55.000 --> 00:15:58.000
I MEAN, THEY'RE--
A LOT OF THIS IS COMPUTERIZED,

00:15:58.000 --> 00:16:02.000
AND YOU PROBABLY DO WANT
SOMEBODY WHO IS WELL--

00:16:02.000 --> 00:16:05.000
MUCH BETTER-EDUCATED
THAN YOU USED TO DEMAND

00:16:05.000 --> 00:16:07.000
OF A POLICEMAN
WALKING THE BEAT.

