00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:08.000
ON THE QUESTION
OF IMMIGRANT INTEGRATION,

00:17:08.000 --> 00:17:10.000
AS IF IT'LL HAPPEN BY MAGIC.

00:17:10.000 --> 00:17:12.000
SO WE'RE SPENDING
BILLIONS OF DOLLARS

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:15.000
ON OUR IMMIGRATION SYSTEM,
AND WE DON'T HAVE ONE PERSON,

00:17:15.000 --> 00:17:17.000
NOT ONE PERSON
IN THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT,

00:17:17.000 --> 00:17:21.000
WHOSE JOB IT IS TO THEN
TAKE A LOOK ACROSS THE COUNTRY

00:17:21.000 --> 00:17:23.000
AND SAY, SO WHAT'S HAPPENING,

00:17:23.000 --> 00:17:25.000
NOW THAT
WE'VE LET THESE PEOPLE IN?

00:17:25.000 --> 00:17:28.000
MR. TEITELBAUM,
AS WE ENTER THE 21st CENTURY,

00:17:28.000 --> 00:17:30.000
THERE SEEMS TO BE
A HEATED DEBATE

00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:34.000
ON WHAT THE AMERICAN NATIONAL
AND ETHNIC IDENTITY SHOULD BE.

