YOU WILL ALWAYS HAVE PEOPLE
WITH NATIONAL IDENTITIES,

00:17:57.000 --> 00:18:02.000
OR ETHNIC IDENTITIES,
OR RELIGIOUS IDENTITIES

00:18:02.000 --> 00:18:04.000
THAT DIFFER FROM ONE ANOTHER,

