AND I THINK
AMERICAN HISTORY HAS SHOWN

00:18:07.000 --> 00:18:10.000
THAT THESE PEOPLE
CAN LIVE TOGETHER SUCCESSFULLY,

00:18:10.000 --> 00:18:13.000
WORK TOGETHER SUCCESSFULLY,
