00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:17.000
IF THEY SHARE
A COMMON SET OF VALUES,

00:18:17.000 --> 00:18:20.000
A COMMON SET
OF NATIONAL IDENTITY,

00:18:20.000 --> 00:18:24.000
IN ADDITION
