AND SO THERE ARE CERTAIN THINGS
THAT IMMIGRANTS ARE LOOKING AT

00:20:05.000 --> 00:20:08.000
IN TERMS OF THE DOMINANT CULTURE
HERE, AND SAYING, WAIT A MINUTE,

00:20:08.000 --> 00:20:11.000
I WANT TO PASS ALONG A DIFFERENT
SET OF VALUES TO MY KIDS.

00:20:11.000 --> 00:20:14.000
