00:21:25.000 --> 00:21:28.000
AND INCLUDED, YOU KNOW,
WITH OTHER WHITES.

00:21:28.000 --> 00:21:32.000
SO RACE IS
A VERY CHANGING CONCEPT,

00:21:32.000 --> 00:21:37.000
IT'S A VERY MALLEABLE CONCEPT,
AND CATEGORIES THAT EXIST TODAY

00:21:37.000 --> 00:21:40.000
ARE UNLIKELY TO EXIST
IN 30 TO 40 YEARS,

00:21:40.000 --> 00:21:43.000
ESPECIALLY GIVEN
THE HIGH RATES OF INTERMARRIAGE.

00:21:46.000 --> 00:21:50.000
OVER ONE-HALF
OF ASIAN WOMEN OUT-MARRY, OK?

00:21:50.000 --> 00:21:54.000
AND CLOSE TO ONE-HALF
OF HISPANICS OUT-MARRY.

00:21:54.000 --> 00:21:57.000
GIVEN THESE
HIGH RATES OF OUT-MARRIAGE,

00:21:57.000 --> 00:22:03.000
THE CURRENT RACIAL DEFINITIONS
ARE GOING TO BE QUITE INADEQUATE

00:22:03.000 --> 00:22:05.000
IN THE COMING DECADES.

