TODAY, THERE ARE
16 DIFFERENT RACIAL CATEGORIES.

00:22:21.000 --> 00:22:23.000
THE CATEGORIES OF RACE

00:22:23.000 --> 00:22:25.000
HAVE ALWAYS INTERESTED
 SOCIAL SCIENTISTS.

00:22:25.000 --> 00:22:28.000
BUT THEIR POLITICAL IMPORTANCE
 INCREASES DRAMATICALLY

00:22:28.000 --> 00:22:30.000
WHEN THESE CATEGORIES ARE USED

00:22:30.000 --> 00:22:32.000
TO AWARD
 PRIVILEGES OR BENEFITS.

